title: 2 Bed apartment in Dripping Springs with Majestic Nature Views
posting_body: ['With the breathtaking Texas Hill Country as a beautiful backdrop, this is your perfect retreat.', 'Impressive interiors inspired by nature reflect a rustic-chic vibe, and captivating amenity spaces provide you with the best of both worlds: all of the conveniences of a resort combined with all of the comforts of home.', 'Our premier location is close to incredible retail venues, vibrant outdoor entertainment, and is within a highly rated school district.', 'Lay your head peacefully in this serene environment now.', 'This locator gives money back rebates of $50-$250.00!', 'Ask me how!', 'Text 2I0-355-7852', 'Christena Barry - Award Winning Locator & Realtor', 'Spirit Real Estate Group', 'ID:  24', '*Pics show general property, not necessarily particular unit.', '*Prices, availability, & specials subject to change.']
